It's one in roughly 261,000.

194
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:41,280
Peanuts themselves have killed
far more people in the last decade

195
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:44,080
than terrorist refugees.

196
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:47,000
