lover, just 10 years younger again,

227
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,600
that man is currently functioning

228
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:45,240
as an effective moral compass
for our politicians.

229
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,360
And now this.

